# Lesson 1.2

# Why Solana Is the Best Chain for Memecoins

Memecoin trading requires **speed and low fees**.

Solana dominates memecoin trading for several reasons.

---

## 1 — Extremely Low Fees

Solana fees are almost zero.

Example from the guide:

Solana trade ≈ $0.00025
Ethereum trade ≈ $5–20 

This matters because memecoin trading requires **many trades**.

Cheap fees allow:

• testing many coins
• entering early
• exiting quickly

---

## 2 — Lightning Fast Transactions

Solana transactions finalize in about **400 milliseconds**.

This is critical because memecoins can move **300% in minutes**. 

Slow chains make you miss the move.

