Solana created a full memecoin environment.

Tools include:

• Pump.fun
• Axiom
• BullX
• Dexscreener
• Phantom wallet 

These tools make launching and trading memes extremely easy.

---

## 4 — High Liquidity

Liquidity allows traders to enter and exit positions easily.

Most Solana memecoins launch with:

$5k – $20k liquidity. 

Large ones reach millions.

