# Lesson 1.3

# The Memecoin Lifecycle

Almost every memecoin follows the same pattern.

Your guide describes **4 phases**. 

---

## Phase 1 — Launch

The coin is created.

Typical signals:

• under 100 holders
• very low market cap
• little social activity

Risk is very high.

Most coins die here.

---

## Phase 2 — Hype

This is the **best entry phase**.

Signals:

• growing social media attention
• increasing holders
• rising volume

Price often rises **50–200%** here.

---

## Phase 3 — Pump

FOMO begins.

Signals:

• price rises extremely fast
• influencers talk about it
• volume explodes

At this stage, smart traders **start taking profits**.

---

## Phase 4 — Dump

Early buyers exit.

Signals:

• declining volume
• large sell orders
• community sentiment changes

Most traders lose money here.

---

## Key Strategy

The **sweet spot** is entering during the **Hype phase**.

Not launch.
Not pump.

---

