# Lesson 1.6

# Crypto Market Cycles

Crypto markets move in cycles.

Your guide explains a typical **4-year cycle**. 

---

## Market Phases

Bear Market
Prices fall for 2–3 years.

Pre-Bull Phase
Market begins recovering.

Bull Market
Prices rise strongly.

Euphoria Phase
Huge speculation and fast gains.

---

Memecoins explode during **late bull market phases**.

This is when:

• new traders enter
• memes go viral
• risk appetite increases

